: 3.317603537629675e-10, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2236, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999145529755902, \"rank\": 8.545389296436431e-05, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's why every left-wing group in America is apoplectic over Louisiana's recent decision to require that the Ten Commandments be posted in Louisiana classrooms; and Oklahoma's decision to make teaching of the Bible mandatory in public schools.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2312, \"end\": 2321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8005273214988238e-12, \"text\": \"Louisiana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\"}, {\"begin\": 2390, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8005273214988238e-12, \"text\": \"Louisiana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\"}, {\"begin\": 2416, \"end\": 2424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma\", \"score\": 0.9994322943395962, \"rank\": 0.0005679784414174289, \"text\": \"Oklahoma\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every left-wing group\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ten Commandments\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"teaching\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bible mandatory\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"public schools\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And why the president of France, Emmanuel Macron, praised his country's opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics, posting on X: \\\"Thanks to Thomas Jolly (the artistic director) and his creative genius for this grandiose ceremony.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2521, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"score\": 0.7348343851884511, \"rank\": 0.3581038710623919, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9995330717530839, \"rank\": 0.00046708132246047585, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"his country's opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"the artistic director\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"his creative genius\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"this grandiose ceremony\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you to the artists for this unique and magical moment.\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the artists\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"this unique and magical moment\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"...\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you to everyone who believed in it.\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will talk about it again in 100 years!\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100 years\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WE DID IT!\\\"\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And there is more bad news: As of this writing, the head of the Catholic Church, Pope Francis, has said nothing about the Olympics' degradation of the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 3049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999701940401, \"rank\": 2.9788566806707046e-08, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 2967, \"end\": 2979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pope Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more bad news\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"this writing\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics' degradation\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3029}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps he was too busy preparing another encyclical about climate change.\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is crucial to note that the Left, whether in America or Europe, never mocks Islam.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Left\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3161}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3181}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"Islam\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One would think that with virtually all religious violence in the world emanating from that religion, the Left would concentrate its antireligious fire against Islam, or at least fundamentalist Islam.\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3391, \"end\": 3411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_fundamentalism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"fundamentalist Islam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_fundamentalism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_fundamentalism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3215}, {\"ngram\": \"virtually all religious violence\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"the world emanating\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"that religion\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3312}, {\"ngram\": \"the Left\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"its antireligious fire\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3363}, {\"ngram\": \"Islam\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why does not it?\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One reason is that leftists fear Muslims.\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3465, \"end\": 3472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.9901490836629743, \"rank\": 0.009948848185131712, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One reason\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"leftists\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you mock Islam, you will have to spend your life in hiding or risk being beheaded.\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Islam\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3491}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"hiding\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other hand, the Left has no fear of Christians.\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3603, \"end\": 3613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9931681414043927, \"rank\": 0.006101472430751102, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other hand\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"the Left\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3587}, {\"ngram\": \"no fear\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No matter how much the Left mocks and undermines Christianity, the Left assumes that not one of the world's two and half billion Christians will hurt them.\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3744, \"end\": 3754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9931681414043927, \"rank\": 0.006101472430751102, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"h